summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2509, for the improvement of 15th Avenue South from Dakota Street to Snoqualmie Street, et al, by watermains, under Ordinance No. 28668 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
